  "priceJustification": {
    "breakEvenDays": 120,
    "roiMultiple": 12,
    "valueProposition": "Automated compliance solutions directly address the multi-million dollar annual risks of 'not knowing.' By streamlining processes, reducing manual errors, and providing real-time visibility, they cut operational inefficiencies, mitigate severe regulatory penalties and warning letters, accelerate time-to-market for critical products, and prevent costly audit failures. The investment of $500-$2000/month (avg. $15,000/year) typically pays for itself in under 4 months through direct efficiency gains alone, delivering an annual ROI multiple exceeding 12x by transforming compliance from a burdensome overhead into a strategic, measurable business asset that drives growth and shareholder value."
  },
